  ## Usage
  * The template includes a summary of the total number of results and pagination pages.
  * Pagination controls will appear when there are more than 10 results.
  * Each result shows the page/document title, its address and an excerpt.
  * The excerpt can highlight relevant portions of the page&rsquo;s content or show the page&rsquo;s description.